Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.80,0:00:06.44,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,For some odd reason, it felt like something was amiss.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.33,0:00:12.19,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,On TV, there was a match between two teams that I had never heard of before,{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.07,0:00:16.92,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,but for some odd reason, I felt compelled to cheer for the losing team.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.92,0:00:21.36,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,And, again for some odd reason, I had the feeling that Haruhi was about to cause a commotion again.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.75,0:00:23.04,Phone,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(345,282)\frz349\blur1}Incoming: Suzumiya Haruhi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.54,0:00:24.82,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,How did I know that?{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.49,0:00:27.26,Haruhi,Imouto,0000,0000,0000,,Kyon-kun, the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.26,0:00:28.92,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to tell me. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.42,0:00:30.93,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,You're free today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.93,0:00:32.88,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,We're all meeting in front of the station at exactly 2 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.88,0:00:33.66,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you come!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.23,0:00:38.41,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't even get to say a thing.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.90,0:00:40.74,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.74,0:00:42.71,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to tell you what to bring.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.71,0:00:45.48,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,Bring your swimming gear and lots of money!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.48,0:00:48.41,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,And make sure you go there on a bike. Over!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.79,0:00:50.17,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.79,0:00:56.45,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Once again, for some odd reason I have this feeling that I knew exactly what Haruhi was going to say.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.45,0:00:57.90,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.90,0:01:02.01,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,More accurately, I get the feeling that the exact same thing had happened before.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.37,0:01:04.53,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what they call "deja vu"?{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.28,0:01:13.28,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Summer is going to end soon, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.25,0:02:52.29,Haruhi Titles,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,580)\pos(358,385)}Endless \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nEight
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.30,0:02:50.52,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, Kyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.93,0:02:52.48,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,You need to show more enthusiasm!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.84,0:02:53.98,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:56.18,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for making you guys wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.18,0:02:57.99,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,I just got here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.99,0:03:00.49,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,Since everyone is here, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.86,0:03:01.24,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,To where?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.58,0:03:03.74,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,To the public pool, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.74,0:03:05.74,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since we brought all this, I guess we would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.60,0:03:09.74,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's summer, we should have summer activities like what other people do in the summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:13.08,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,We're never going to get back the time we lost, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:15.02,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we're doing this right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.39,0:03:18.34,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,This is our once-in-a-lifetime freshman summer vacation!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.87,0:03:21.18,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, we're going to the pool by bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.67,0:03:23.22,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me you guys brought your bikes too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.49,0:03:26.68,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,No. You and I are the only ones who brought bikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.48,0:03:30.51,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,Got it, Kyon?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.51,0:03:32.06,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,You can't lose to Koizumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:34.02,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,Now, commence take off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:34.73,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.99,0:03:40.73,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and get off your bikes, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.73,0:03:43.11,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,We came here to have fun! Why are you two worn out already?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:45.37,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Whose fault do you think it is? Whose?!{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:54.46,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the smell of chlorine! This is what it's all about!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.29,0:04:01.73,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.73,0:04:03.30,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,The water is nice and warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.85,0:04:06.63,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Can't she see the signs that say "No Diving"?{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.27,0:04:08.70,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like fun, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:11.29,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite a pleasant scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.29,0:04:13.23,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Also, it's peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.17,0:04:18.87,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think Suzumiya-san may have found a normal way of enjoying things?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.87,0:04:23.55,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,She called me to go out all of a sudden, and then hung up on me after stating her one-sided demands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.55,0:04:25.28,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,You can't exactly say that's normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.58,0:04:26.70,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Really now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:29.53,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,If you want me to be the one calling you, I'll gladly do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.53,0:04:35.08,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing her having so much fun, there shouldn't be anything happening that will endanger the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:38.42,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,If only that were true...{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.87,0:04:40.92,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.73,0:04:44.76,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. It's probably just my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.17,0:04:47.24,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,We've been through all sorts of things since spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.24,0:04:49.45,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I think I might have become a little neurotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.53,0:05:01.60,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot!{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.81,0:05:04.00,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot!{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.00,0:05:05.56,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,It's hooooot!{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.81,0:05:13.66,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Man, it'd be more appropriate to call this place a "pool for the masses" than a "pool for the public".{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:16.71,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Haruhi choose this kind of place anyway?{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.45,0:05:26.13,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting that feeling again.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.71,0:05:29.89,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I've seen this somewhere before.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.59,0:05:33.46,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,For some odd reason, Nagato looks like she's bored.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.41,0:05:36.13,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,Kyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.85,0:05:42.23,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Then Haruhi said something like...{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.47,0:05:44.86,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,These two are my brigade members.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:46.52,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,They'll listen to everything I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.52,0:05:47.78,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,So ask them anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.73,0:05:50.61,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.61,0:05:52.60,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to play water soccer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:53.41,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:56.62,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Well, deja vu happens all the time, I guess.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:05:58.04,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come, Mikuru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.34,0:05:58.99,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:07.72,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,I came up with an action plan for the rest of summer. What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.29,0:06:10.22,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,All of this in less than two weeks.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.50,0:06:12.82,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikuru-chan, do you have anything you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.82,0:06:16.21,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, I would like to scoop up goldfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.21,0:06:18.95,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Goldfish scooping it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:20.19,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:26.86,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.21,0:06:28.83,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,We'll start tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.83,0:06:31.29,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if there's an Obon festival being held near here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.29,0:06:33.28,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,A fireworks festival would be nice too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.28,0:06:34.87,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll look into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:37.37,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget the goldfish scooping!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:39.33,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,It's Mikuru-chan's one passionate desire, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.69,0:06:41.08,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.91,0:06:43.79,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one paying again...{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.70,0:06:46.71,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's it for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:47.69,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's it for me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.69,0:06:48.73,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.04,0:07:04.85,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Nagato!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:13.38,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no. It's nothing really...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.79,0:07:15.14,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,How've you been feeling lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.14,0:07:16.33,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,You okay and everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.91,0:07:17.83,Haruhi,Nagato,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:19.12,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.41,0:07:24.08,Haruhi,Nagato,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.65,0:07:30.44,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Why?{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:32.53,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I call out to her?{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.34,0:07:35.47,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,The next morning.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:38.88,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,The call that stole my indolence away was, once again, from Haruhi.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:41.51,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,We've figured out where they're going to have the Obon festival:{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.51,0:07:43.65,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight at the public sports ground.{TH} {was "Civic Stadium" in the previous ep though =/}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:50.90,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to buy yukatas together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.59,0:07:54.24,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Haruhi led us into a bulk clothing store,{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:56.61,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,personally chose Asahina-san and Nagato's yukatas,{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.61,0:07:58.73,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,and then immediately proceeded to drag them into the changing rooms.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.73,0:08:00.87,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,After making us wait for nearly an hour,{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.87,0:08:03.04,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,the three of them finally returned.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.86,0:08:06.50,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Woah, they look great on you girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.72,0:08:09.38,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! I picked them out, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:10.88,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,Especially Mikuru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.17,0:08:13.68,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cute! Just what I'd expect from myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:15.18,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.50,0:08:17.60,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Turning red triples your cuteness!{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:27.97,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Bon dancing, huh? It attracts quite the crowd.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.56,0:08:32.52,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,It should be my first time in a while,{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.52,0:08:34.47,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,so why do I get the feeling that I've been here just recently?{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.07,0:08:36.12,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,That stage...{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:37.70,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,That food stall...{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:38.78,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikuru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:41.66,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,They have the goldfish scooping that you wanted to do over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.66,0:08:43.33,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's scoop non-stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.33,0:08:43.93,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.47,0:08:49.95,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we do the same? How about a little competition?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.95,0:08:50.92,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:54.64,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Aside from that, Nagato, do you want to get something to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.51,0:09:17.66,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,You're interested in that stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:19.33,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Which do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.33,0:09:20.06,Haruhi,Nagato,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.24,0:09:22.97,Haruhi,Nagato,0000,0000,0000,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.97,0:09:23.76,Haruhi,Storekeeper,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:24.91,Haruhi,Storekeeper,0000,0000,0000,,That's 800 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.24,0:09:32.79,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,For some odd reason, I feel like she's been looking after me, so paying for that would've been fine, but...{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.93,0:09:36.91,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,Man, we had a huge catch today! Huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.33,0:09:40.22,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,But we just took one because we didn't need all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:42.22,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,And another one for Mikuru too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:47.89,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay for you to have one. {rephrasing is needed. I tried to go for as close as possible compared to what we had in ep 2, but the situation was kinda different, so it was a bit hard.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.33,0:09:50.35,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.96,0:10:00.16,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yuki, what's with the mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.18,0:10:02.24,Haruhi,Nagato,0000,0000,0000,,I bought it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.68,0:10:04.34,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.22,0:10:08.67,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Fireworks are next! Fireworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:10.13,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do that to finish the day off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.01,0:10:14.55,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you ever heard of the saying "Don’t bite off more than you can chew"?{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.81,0:10:17.80,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,When it's summer, there's summer vacation.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.53,0:10:23.68,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,So if I could have, I'd rather have forgotten about it, but I came to realize something.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.08,0:10:28.10,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go bug catching tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:31.81,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Haruhi, having fun is great and all, but have you finished your homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:32.89,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.89,0:10:35.80,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,I finished all of that in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.80,0:10:36.19,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Three days?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:42.86,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,Finish off all that tedious stuff so you can actually enjoy yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.86,0:10:45.68,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,That's the right way to enjoy summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.13,0:10:48.66,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Why is this person so smart?{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.02,0:10:55.14,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,The distribution of attributes is pretty random.{TH} {Again, matched the last 4 lines with ep 2}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:10:57.80,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:10:59.98,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,We're catching bugs tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.98,0:11:04.30,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,The person who catches the most will be Brigade Chief for one day!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.40,0:11:04.86,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.19,0:11:06.78,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.78,0:11:08.26,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,So it counts as long as it's any kind of bug?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.67,0:11:09.68,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.68,0:11:10.77,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,Cicadas only!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.04,0:11:13.31,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. This will be the SOS Brigade's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.31,0:11:15.11,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,Cicada Catching Competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.67,0:11:20.53,Thoughts,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,The next day, we got what you could call a ridiculously nice day.{TH} {We actually ignored the Nihon-bare part in the previous episode. Not sure if you want to leave that in. We used “ridiculously nice day” instead.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.53,0:11:23.23,Thoughts,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,The participants fought valiantly, but...{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.23,0:11:26.83,Thoughts,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,For some familiar reason or another, the winner was Haruhi.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:30.25,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,We should go with a "catch-and-release" mentality.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:34.04,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,They might repay us with a favor in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.26,0:11:37.09,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,And what exactly can a cicada do for us?{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.34,0:11:39.59,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,Here, go back to the mountains!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.27,0:11:50.11,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason, it felt like we were opening Pandora's Box.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.84,0:11:55.56,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.56,0:11:59.89,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,The next day, we were gathered for some random reason,{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.89,0:12:02.57,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,given a bunch of random frog costumes,{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:06.57,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,and ended up handing out balloons in front of a supermarket as a small part-time job.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:10.40,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your work everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.15,0:12:13.14,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Why are being we treated like slaves?{TH} {lit. what's with this kind of treatment?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.14,0:12:14.36,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.36,0:12:16.25,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,The manager was really grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:18.30,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need the old man's gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:19.23,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Where's our pay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.57,0:12:20.27,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.27,0:12:20.55,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.91,0:12:23.57,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,I've wanted this for a while now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.57,0:12:25.93,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,He said he’d give it to us because of Mikuru-chan! {XD, we seriously went with Uncle in the episode 02? BTW, Jackie Chen called and “You kill my uncle, I no forgive you!”}{Uncle issue resolved}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.47,0:12:30.06,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,You made us do all that work just for the sake of getting that?{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.29,0:12:32.43,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's decorate the clubroom with this in commemoration!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.69,0:12:36.05,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikuru-chan, you can wear it whenever you feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.05,0:12:37.56,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,I give you my permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.40,0:12:46.72,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,That night.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.72,0:12:50.68,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,My slumber was once again stolen away by none other than a phone call.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.92,0:12:52.77,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Damnit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.05,0:12:59.79,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,Kyon-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.12,0:13:02.27,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Asahina-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.29,0:13:05.31,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.67,0:13:08.00,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,Something bad has...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.00,0:13:09.69,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,If this goes on... I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.37,0:13:12.81,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.07,0:13:14.27,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hello. It's me, Koizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:18.65,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you together with Asahina-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.31,0:13:21.14,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,A slight problem has occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.60,0:13:23.65,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you could come here right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.04,0:13:25.25,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be there immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.25,0:13:26.15,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:33.01,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly happened, Asahina-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.83,0:13:37.50,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,Uuu, Kyon-kun... {Do we need this UUUUUUU shit? >.>}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:38.65,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:45.98,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go back to the future anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.29,0:13:55.93,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,In short, that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.82,0:14:00.12,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,We're currently looping through the same period of time over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.12,0:14:03.44,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,For something so absurdly unrealistic, you said that quite cheerfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.76,0:14:06.52,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi, do you have any idea what you're saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.09,0:14:08.45,Haruhi,Koizumi,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:10.20,Haruhi,Koizumi,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing more to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.50,0:14:13.01,Haruhi,Koizumi,0000,0000,0000,,I was talking to Asahina-san just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:14.95,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Call me up too! For that sort of meeting.{TH} {Re-TLC PLEASE} {Re-TLC'd}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.23,0:14:19.96,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, I happened to notice that the flow of time has felt strange lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.48,0:14:23.41,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Asahina-san was the one who discovered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.41,0:14:25.21,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to that, I was able to confirm something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.61,0:14:26.97,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Confirm what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.54,0:14:31.90,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,We're experiencing a repeat of the same time over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.90,0:14:33.35,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,You told me that already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.70,0:14:37.96,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,To be precise, the loop occurs from August 11th to August 31st.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:40.27,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's an endless summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.67,0:14:45.30,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,The world now has lost all time past September 1st.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.09,0:14:49.27,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's the reason why Asahina-san is unable to return to the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.27,0:14:50.61,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's only natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.96,0:14:53.84,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,What part of physics argues that a state of "No Future" is natural?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.84,0:14:55.37,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell would believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.64,0:14:58.77,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping that you would believe it, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.77,0:15:02.20,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I'll give you an explanation too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:07.68,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I use *classified information* to communicate with the future
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.68,0:15:10.41,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,and do things dealing with *classified information*.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:15.95,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,For a week, I've had no *classified information*, so I thought:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.38,0:15:17.58,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,"This is strange..."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.58,0:15:19.69,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,And then *classified information*.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.37,0:15:24.71,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,I was really surprised, so I did *classified information* out of panic,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.02,0:15:28.57,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,but it was completely *classified information*...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:30.56,Haruhi,Mikuru,0000,0000,0000,,I... Why? {Let’s considering putting classified information in square brackets}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.56,0:15:33.50,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you ask me why, I have no idea.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:37.37,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Was she just using the term "classified information" as a replacement for censoring words?{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.05,0:15:42.36,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Are we trapped inside something similar to an enclosed space?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:45.75,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:49.48,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,One part of the time continuum has just been cut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.33,0:15:53.79,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,When we reach August 31st, everything will be reset at exactly 2400 hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.79,0:15:58.39,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,and we will return to August 11th again. That's the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.68,0:16:01.89,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,So what about our... no, the memories belonging to the entire human race?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.12,0:16:03.69,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,That also gets reset.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.03,0:16:06.19,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Everything starts over from the beginning again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:08.51,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,And then time replays itself again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:12.07,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I get the feeling that it can't be helped, since people from the future are involved with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.07,0:16:15.09,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,No. This one has nothing to do with Asahina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.09,0:16:16.41,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Then who's the cause of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.78,0:16:18.06,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Probably Suzumiya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.63,0:16:22.42,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,She might be unaware of it herself, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.42,0:16:26.88,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,a part of her might not want summer to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:28.33,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.33,0:16:29.84,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Does she have some sort of regret?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.39,0:16:31.87,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I believe so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.87,0:16:36.09,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,It may very well be the fact that she feels like she still has something she needs to do during summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.32,0:16:40.59,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Way to blow some meaningless, small issue into galactic proportions.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.94,0:16:42.35,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,So what do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.71,0:16:45.71,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,If I knew, I would have already resolved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.71,0:16:46.86,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,You're too close.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.17,0:16:48.60,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking this for a while now,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.12,0:16:50.61,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,but you're having fun, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.67,0:16:53.61,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,You are too, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.09,0:16:58.24,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally managed to solve the riddle of deja vu being left as imprints from past loops.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:16:59.67,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.67,0:17:04.90,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to understand that the imprints are simply what you would call the remains of a memory reset.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.87,0:17:08.88,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me that everyone else in the world feels it too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.11,0:17:10.84,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:13.14,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,You and I are special cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.62,0:17:15.77,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Just by being close to Suzumiya-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.77,0:17:18.28,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,we've become the only ones capable of feeling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.18,0:17:20.66,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,What about Haruhi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.66,0:17:22.91,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,She isn't the least bit aware of this fact?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.91,0:17:25.30,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look like it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.30,0:17:27.27,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,It would probably be a lot more complicated if she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:30.07,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that, with the deja vu,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.07,0:17:35.65,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking that there must be someone who has retained all of his or her memories of the repeated time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.18,0:17:38.11,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,And who would that someone be?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.56,0:17:40.07,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I think you'll know without me having to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.61,0:17:41.78,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's Nagato-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:45.16,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Being outside the constraints of space and time,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:47.36,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,the Integrated Data Sentient Entity most likely knows the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.76,0:17:49.75,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Is this true?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.01,0:17:50.46,Haruhi,Nagato,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.57,0:17:53.42,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.85,0:17:54.42,Haruhi,Nagato,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.82,0:17:58.16,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Out of curiosity, how many times have we been "reset"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.56,0:18:02.22,Haruhi,Nagato,0000,0000,0000,,This is the fifteen thousand, four hundred and ninety eighth time we've had this discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.72,0:18:06.93,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Fifteen thousand, four hundred and ninety eight?{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.93,0:18:09.63,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by 15,498?{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.63,0:18:11.48,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Nagato, what are you talking about?{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.25,0:18:14.19,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Are you being serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.43,0:18:15.21,Haruhi,Nagato,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.98,0:18:20.43,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,So we did the same thing over and over again each and every one of those times?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.43,0:18:22.59,Haruhi,Nagato,0000,0000,0000,,That is not necessarily the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.59,0:18:25.22,Haruhi,Nagato,0000,0000,0000,,In the last 15,498 times,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.22,0:18:27.71,Haruhi,Nagato,0000,0000,0000,,we did not go to the Obon festival 2,391 of those times.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:31.53,Haruhi,Nagato,0000,0000,0000,,Another 11,054 times, we went twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.53,0:18:36.54,Haruhi,Nagato,0000,0000,0000,,Also, Obon minus the goldfish scooping occurred 437 times.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.54,0:18:39.48,Haruhi,Nagato,0000,0000,0000,,Part-time work has been conducted a total of 9,025 times.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.48,0:18:40.76,Haruhi,Nagato,0000,0000,0000,,Among which there have been six variations-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:42.72,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.47,0:18:51.69,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,15,498 times. That's what Nagato said.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.69,0:18:56.48,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Times the 2 weeks is... uhh, about 594 years.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.34,0:19:04.21,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Was she simply enduring all that time alone, living it over and over again while retaining her memories?{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.81,0:19:09.71,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Nagato, just how does it feel to have lived through all of this?{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.18,0:19:18.76,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up hearing something ridiculous again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.47,0:19:21.76,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,The next day was stargazing.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.27,0:19:24.81,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,The venue was the rooftop of Nagato's apartment.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.81,0:19:27.77,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi prepared the telescope.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.76,0:19:29.95,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they're there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.95,0:19:30.56,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:31.35,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,Martians.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.35,0:19:32.65,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really want them to exist.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.02,0:19:35.29,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like there's no one on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.29,0:19:38.21,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,They might just be a timid people that live underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.21,0:19:39.69,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,They're probably a friendly bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.69,0:19:40.90,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that could happen.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.34,0:19:43.89,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,The day humans first set foot on Mars,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.89,0:19:47.17,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,they'll definitely come out of their caves and welcome humans as a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.17,0:19:48.91,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,They'll say "Welcome to Mars!" or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.91,0:19:50.91,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like it'd be mistaken for an attack.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:53.11,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, this is boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.11,0:19:54.92,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's look for UFOs!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.05,0:20:02.58,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly does she want to do, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.58,0:20:04.42,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.42,0:20:06.97,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Once we figure that out, this problem will be relatively straightforward to solve.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.28,0:20:10.02,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we try this out for starters?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.58,0:20:13.42,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly hug Suzumiya-san from behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:16.64,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,and whisper in her ear: "I love you".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.13,0:20:18.83,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,And who's doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:21.64,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one more suitable than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.30,0:20:24.95,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to exercise my right to veto!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.47,0:20:26.50,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass on this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.26,0:20:30.54,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I do it then?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.26,0:20:35.87,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.87,0:20:37.74,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not qualified for that role.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.47,0:20:41.22,Haruhi,Itsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I would only put Suzumiya-san into an unnecessary state of confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.18,0:20:52.56,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,The next place we went to was the batting center.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.74,0:21:02.90,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nagato.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.57,0:21:05.84,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Even before you talked to Asahina-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.84,0:21:07.84,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,you already realized everything was repeating, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.32,0:21:08.95,Haruhi,Nagato,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.65,0:21:12.41,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,So why did you keep quiet about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.93,0:21:15.91,Haruhi,Nagato,0000,0000,0000,,My mission is to observe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.08,0:21:22.28,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.94,0:21:26.34,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,The string of vigorous summer vacation events continued.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.11,0:21:29.71,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,And we continued to be carried away along with them.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.06,0:21:34.22,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I knew that this still wouldn't leave Haruhi satisfied,{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.22,0:21:36.80,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,so I didn't make any effort to do anything.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.80,0:21:40.18,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,While were running around having fun, August 30th arrived.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.26,0:21:43.78,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,With that, we've pretty much completed our summer plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.87,0:21:49.90,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's okay like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.90,0:21:50.79,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.21,0:21:53.67,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.67,0:21:56.04,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do any of you want to do anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.69,0:22:00.92,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.92,0:22:04.80,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,We've already done so much this summer, so it's probably enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.74,0:22:07.17,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,No. This isn't fine.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.92,0:22:10.22,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't supposed to be satisfied yet!{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.47,0:22:12.48,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's call it a day then.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.80,0:22:16.68,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you have tomorrow off to prepare for school.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.68,0:22:19.28,Haruhi,Haruhi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's meet in the club room the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.64,0:22:22.48,Haruhi,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Haruhi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.74,0:22:24.72,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,This again...{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.72,0:22:25.44,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Deja vu!{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.57,0:22:29.64,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,And this feels stronger than before.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.21,0:22:32.16,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let Haruhi go home like this!{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.16,0:22:33.36,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,If I let her go home now,{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.36,0:22:38.16,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,all those ten thousand something weeks will just end up being repeated again!{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.56,0:22:40.67,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,But what should I do?{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.93,0:22:42.51,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,What should I say?{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.00,0:22:46.05,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,There should be hints in Haruhi's words!{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.30,0:22:47.63,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,But what are they?{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.32,0:22:50.29,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,What did she say until now?{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.17,0:22:53.18,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.51,0:22:54.85,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,I can't remember...{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.25,0:23:05.10,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,August 31st.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.51,0:23:07.14,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Homework: unfinished.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.07,0:23:09.37,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care anymore.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.37,0:23:10.60,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever happens, happens.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.72,0:23:17.85,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,If it really does repeat again,{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.85,0:23:20.66,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,doing this homework would be meaningless.{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.72,0:23:23.66,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we happen to get to tomorrow...{TH}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.16,0:23:27.26,Thoughts,Kyon,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll just have to leave it to myself to figure out later.{TH}
